latestPosts.caption:
Second Sunday of the weekly zine challenge and my heart is soooo warm, because this zine is the story of @walkwithm_  and her partner @akshayxy .
A story wrapped in love, fur and realities of rescue.🐾🐾
In a world where we make excuses for little things, they remind me that there’s simply no excuse for not doing what you believe in.
Everyday, every second, mindfully dedicated with such ease in protecting what they believe inn.

In a world where we question humanity everyday, they look like super humans to me.

Why this zine exists?
To remind you that - it only takes small acts of kindess.
I hope you take a pause, i hope makes sense.
 And also to Thank them for encouraging more humans silently, fiercely, without applause.

So today, tomorrow, day after-
Support a rescuer.
Share their posts.
Adopt.
Donate.
Volunteer.
Love. 
The three individual rescuers that  @walkwithm_ wants to put focus on and that I know are doing tiring work are 
picturekahero- Indore
@tug_n_shred_crew - Bangalore 
@himalayantails - Uttrakhand

latestPosts.caption:
Art department ka jhola itna bada kyu hota he?
 special thanks to my @aashkathakker for recording this and sharing the weight of this bag 🩷

REMIMDERS FOR FELLOW ARTISTS:
1)ART TAKES TIME.
2)ART IS NOT PERFECT.
3)JUST BECAUSE IT’s NOT YOUR BEST WORK, DOES’nt MEAN IT’s BAD.
4)WHEN YOU CREATE ART FOR A LIVING, JUGAAD KEEPS YOU IN BUDGET, ART ON A BUDGET CAN ALSO BE REWARDING🤌🏻
5)NEVER STOP CREATING🩷

Gentle reminder for fellow artists with my Udaipur Art Gang @bhavinnn.af  @neerajnarnolia_06

latestPosts.caption:
As young girl, i wanted to travel, TRAVEL ALOT, and create my art in new places as i dwell in the beauty of new landscapes..
Every single day i wake up and work to make that happen.
Today I’m truly grateful for what i’ve build, grateful for the places my work takes me to, grateful for a family that supports this crazy lifestyle and has my back, and grateful for this body that show’s up every single time🩷🧿
If i could tell something to my younger self, i’d say; KEEP WORKING HARD AND IT’ll pay off🤌🏻
